-- pyexasol-based install.py, or any Exasol driver) — NOT through MaxScale.
-- The --/ ... / script-block markers and CREATE SCRIPT bodies below are
-- exaplus/Exasol-native and do not survive a MariaDB client + preprocessor.
--
-- exaplus 25.2.6 does not enter script-body mode for CREATE PREPROCESSOR
-- SCRIPT (works fine for SCALAR SCRIPT). The bundle therefore wraps
-- SCALAR UDFs in --/ ... / blocks and emits PREPROCESSOR scripts with
-- a bare trailing `;` — preprocessor source files must keep `;` out of
